Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.93,0:22:15.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爷爷…那个时候是故意的…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.80,0:22:36.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也想在天空中飞翔吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.09,0:22:38.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽情地飞翔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,————————————————————————————
